Summary: Took a picture - the photo shows a UFO
divs: sighting detailssee the photo posted *(link moved to additional evidence section--cms\sg) click the of interest section at the top bar. i was living on the yakima indian reservation on a produce farm. i stayed in a house trailer and was learning auto\tractor mechanics from a person whom also stayed on the farm property. this is located at the end of slough rd. in n. wapato, wa. there were two old cars (the convertable ford is still there) that i decided to get a photo of. i do not believe in 'little voices' that people 'imagine', yet i still remember the 'warning' impulses i received while going to get the photo (don't - you will <><> not don't, etc..) i took a photo, and not until recently looked closely at it. i posted it on my website(above). it was taken on 110 film and looked like a lens or film flaw. not very big, yet, when blown up is a true ufo. the photo has the date on the back, mar 1989.
